videos.headline: Oklahoma State WR catches wide-open TD pass
videos.description: Cowboys QB Taylor Cornelius tosses a 21-yard pass to WR Tylan Wallace, who makes an easy catch in the end zone.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State RB jukes multiple defenders for TD
videos.description: Oklahoma State QB Taylor Cornelius tosses a short pass to RB Chuba Hubbard, who shakes multiple defenders on a 54-yard touchdown play.
